'''Ognyanovo reservoir''', also called '''Lake Ognyanovo''', or '''Ognyanova''', is a reservoir in [[Bulgaria]] near Sofia. Holding 32 million cubic metres of water, it is an important [[List of dams and reservoirs in Bulgaria|reservoir in Bulgaria]]. It impounds the waters of the Lesnovska river.
On October 27, 2011, while the second-unit stunt team was filming a stuntman (Kun Liu) was killed and another (Nuo Sun), was critically injured in a staged explosion on a rubber boat. Sun underwent a five-hour operation, which left him in stable condition.<ref name="FilmingAcc1">{{cite web|url=http://www.sofiaecho.com/2011/10/28/1189640_expendables-2-stuntman-killed-on-ognyanovo-dam |title=Expendables 2 stuntman killed on Ognyanovo dam |publisher=Sofia Echo Media |work=The Sofia Echo |date=October 28, 2011 |accessdate=October 28, 2011 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6BWJHhb3s?url=http://www.sofiaecho.com/2011/10/28/1189640_expendables-2-stuntman-killed-on-ognyanovo-dam |archivedate=October 19, 2012 |deadurl=no |df= }}</ref><ref name="FilmingAcc2">{{cite web|first=Nellie |last=Andreeva |url=http://www.deadline.com/2011/10/stuntman-dies-during-the-filming-of-the-expendables-2/ |title=UPDATE: Stuntmen In ‘Expendables 2′ Fatal Accident Identified |publisher=PMC |work=Deadline.com |date=October 31, 2011 |accessdate=October 31, 2011 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6BWJN8cD2?url=http://www.deadline.com/2011/10/stuntman-dies-during-the-filming-of-the-expendables-2/ |archivedate=October 19, 2012 |deadurl=no |df= }}</ref>
